Password: secret
Pool size: 20

## Features
Caching: true
Telemetry: false
Strict mode: true

## Routes
### Route
Method: GET
Path: /health
Auth: false

### Route
Method: POST
Path: /api/upload
Auth: true
Timeout ms: 15000
